com.readytalk.swt.text.navigation

Class Hyperlink

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.readytalk.swt.text.navigation.Hyperlink

  • public class Hyperlink
extends java.lang.Object
    Hyperlink is a class representing a section of clickable text. It is a composite of a Token, representing a URL, and a rectangular boundary.
